{"tid":1590093,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"10月後路線圖","createTime":"2019-09-23T14:29:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T16:20:54.000Z","uid":294729,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"cc7f8070f86763b6896b3bcdba08b4b7f26fcbf0","tid":1590093,"uid":294729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:29:20.000Z","msg":"P牌仔第一次出po 歡迎討論。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢幾日連登有大量po 話運動開始少人同失焦。不過大家係未唔記得左10月之後其中一個重要既支線任務，就係區議會選舉！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能各位會即刻鬧我係未分化運動係未想散水？你地可能話就算贏左區選，都唔會影響到港共。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係大家唔好唔記得保皇黨班仆街其實好驚輸區選，宜家各個區都已經有我地呢邊既素人出選。如果能夠將大家既力量放起一個明確既目標既話，就可以為呢場運動注入新鮮感同動力，凝聚番個社區力量。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且我地比對家優勝之處係人夠多同埋有唔同年紀，各行各業既人士，所以可以諗多啲唔同形式既助選同造勢活動，例如派傳單、上門探訪、義診義教，提升我地陣營既形象。試諗一下街坊同著住full gear既手足傾計，又或者比佢地見識一下我地點樣保護其他街坊免受藍絲廢老騷擾，個畫面係幾禁震撼！天琦講過我地要做既野係諗點樣令到更多人加入我地，今次就係一個好機會走入社區宣傳運動。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地集中火力去做呢個支線任務唔係整停運動，而係令到大家有動力繼續玩落去，呢場運動預計要持續好耐，如果大家禁快搵唔到動力，運動就會慢慢消亡，到時我地坐監同死去既朋友就絕對唔會原諒我地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我建議選舉完，回完血之後馬上再舉行百萬人大遊行，即係11月30日，話比港共聽我地繼續五大訴求，唔好禁天真以為我地過左區選就收檔！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n認同請幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"503076fe046494132051703bcfa48cc863a9b96f","tid":1590093,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:31:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589858</a>"},{"pid":"fb0690efa3811650ef40e22157e065f484b800c6","tid":1590093,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:31:08.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">十月一 &middot; 港九新界加機場 遍地開花 封哂成個香港丫笨</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">10.1全民舉黑遮大集會，再放手放開所有咁放黑汽球上天</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"8c6d473fa4a9be0d32457f7066bc9a616c63874c","tid":1590093,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:21:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87240dd26e266891d30513f90a8959df7cc9e6e8","tid":1590093,"uid":138427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb0690efa3811650ef40e22157e065f484b800c6","tid":1590093,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:31:08.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">十月一 &middot; 港九新界加機場 遍地開花 封哂成個香港丫笨</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">10.1全民舉黑遮大集會，再放手放開所有咁放黑汽球上天</span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:23:24.000Z","msg":"再放手放開所有咁放黑汽球上天 正"},{"pid":"a71236310779050171e3c641322f438e8081e63a","tid":1590093,"uid":35831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:24:06.000Z","msg":"我係召集今日喺始創唱國歌嗰個小薯仔，我有啲嘢想講<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590080\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590080</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1a2b8bbe9320621f5ff4e85e99c8193f25c8078e","tid":1590093,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:26:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adfcb6799a0e92d4750083bf4597f4b178236110","tid":1590093,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:29:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60d2bc6c1c280ce4205f3c17cdd16a78267f39bf","tid":1590093,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:59:04.000Z","msg":"and then???"},{"pid":"c9eca1d4d404faa8bcc79e6199ed1812e3929b2c","tid":1590093,"uid":158766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T16:04:25.000Z","msg":"香港警察鎮壓騷亂時導致示威者死亡<br />\n<br />\n香港警察扣押示威者時輪姦香港女市民<br />\n<br />\n黑警死三代<br />\n721<br />\n811<br />\n831"},{"pid":"3da5d17417e5ecfc2e8727fb2d685f91cbfec5c8","tid":1590093,"uid":59753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T16:13:37.000Z","msg":"仲係度叫人落社區拉票搞選舉工程 食人血饅頭 咁我地坐監同死去既朋友就真係絕對唔會原諒我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45250fac00cf031b182583cdb0cf965c9aa5d948","tid":1590093,"uid":259973,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3da5d17417e5ecfc2e8727fb2d685f91cbfec5c8","tid":1590093,"uid":59753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T16:13:37.000Z","msg":"仲係度叫人落社區拉票搞選舉工程 食人血饅頭 咁我地坐監同死去既朋友就真係絕對唔會原諒我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T16:20:54.000Z","msg":"唔食之後成班保皇何妖做咗手足先唔會原諒我哋，記唔記得6月定7月早就有勇武講過係要食人血饅頭，本來成個抗爭就係食班坐監同死去嘅手足㗎饅頭，佢哋血流咗你唔食佢哋就係白流。<br />\n區選選咗dq,到時咪俾美國做野囉，又可以升級，仲可以明正言順。冇人話得一條戰線"}]}